msgid ""
"Measure and tune Klein for Ray concurrency, batching, partitioning, "
"buffers, replay, state, checkpoints, and placement."
msgstr "测量并调优 Klein for Ray 的并发、批处理、分区、缓冲区、重放、状态、检查点和放置。"

msgid "Performance tuning"
msgstr "性能调优"

msgid ""
"Tune from measurements, one boundary at a time. Increasing concurrency or"
" buffer capacity can move a bottleneck downstream, increase checkpoint "
"alignment time, and enlarge the replay window without increasing end-to-"
"end throughput."
msgstr "应以测量结果为依据，每次只调优一个边界。提高并发或缓冲区容量可能只是将瓶颈移到下游，增加检查点对齐时间并扩大重放窗口，却无法提高端到端吞吐量。"

msgid "Establish a baseline"
msgstr "建立基线"

msgid ""
"Record the following under representative input, state size, and external"
" service latency:"
msgstr "在具有代表性的输入、状态大小和外部服务延迟下记录以下数据："

msgid "records in/out per operator;"
msgstr "每个算子的输入/输出记录数；"

msgid "processing p50/p95/p99 latency;"
msgstr "处理 p50/p95/p99 延迟；"

msgid "input-buffer utilization and backpressure duration;"
msgstr "输入缓冲区利用率和背压持续时间；"

msgid "source lag and idle inputs;"
msgstr "源延迟和空闲输入；"

msgid "checkpoint duration, alignment time, persistence time, and failures;"
msgstr "检查点持续时间、对齐时间、持久化时间和故障；"

msgid "managed-state size and snapshot/restore duration;"
msgstr "托管状态大小和快照/恢复持续时间；"

msgid "replay-buffer records and bytes;"
msgstr "重放缓冲区中的记录数和字节数；"

msgid ""
"CPU, memory, Object Store pressure, spilling, and network use per Ray "
"node."
msgstr "每个 Ray 节点的 CPU、内存、Object Store 压力、溢写和网络使用量。"

msgid ""
"Use `ray.klein.explain()` to save the logical plan with every benchmark. "
"A different plan or concurrency topology is a different baseline."
msgstr "每次基准测试都使用 `ray.klein.explain()` 保存逻辑计划。不同的计划或并发拓扑应视为不同的基线。"

msgid "Diagnose by symptom"
msgstr "按症状诊断"

msgid "Symptom"
msgstr "症状"

msgid "Inspect first"
msgstr "首先检查"

msgid "Likely actions"
msgstr "建议操作"

msgid "Source lag rises, downstream idle"
msgstr "源延迟上升，下游空闲"

msgid "Source poll duration, assigned partitions, source CPU"
msgstr "源轮询持续时间、已分配分区、源 CPU"

msgid ""
"Increase source concurrency up to useful partitions; increase connector "
"poll batch size; verify broker throttling."
msgstr "将源并发提高到有效分区数；增大连接器轮询批大小；确认 broker 是否限流。"

msgid "One transform is CPU-bound"
msgstr "某个转换受 CPU 限制"

msgid "Operator processing latency and CPU"
msgstr "算子处理延迟和 CPU"

msgid ""
"Increase that operator's concurrency/CPU; use `map_batches`; vectorize "
"the UDF."
msgstr "提高该算子的并发/CPU；使用 `map_batches`；对 UDF 进行向量化。"

msgid "GPU/model calls underutilized"
msgstr "GPU/模型调用利用不足"

msgid "Batch fill time, async pending work, service latency"
msgstr "批次填充时间、异步待处理工作、服务延迟"

msgid ""
"Increase `batch_size` carefully, set a bounded timeout, or use "
"`async_buffer_size`; do not chain async operators."
msgstr "谨慎增大 `batch_size`、设置有界超时，或使用 `async_buffer_size`；不要链接异步算子。"

msgid "High input-buffer utilization"
msgstr "输入缓冲区利用率高"

msgid "Slow downstream operator, write timeout, backpressure metrics"
msgstr "慢速下游算子、写入超时、背压指标"

msgid ""
"Fix the consumer first; then adjust concurrency or batching. Larger "
"buffers only absorb bursts."
msgstr "先修复消费方，再调整并发或批处理。更大的缓冲区只能吸收突发流量。"

msgid "Checkpoints are slow"
msgstr "检查点速度慢"

msgid "Alignment, state snapshot, persistence, sink commit histograms"
msgstr "对齐、状态快照、持久化、sink 提交直方图"

msgid ""
"Reduce skew/in-flight buffers, use local RocksDB, review object-store "
"latency and sink commit time."
msgstr "减少倾斜/在途缓冲，使用本地 RocksDB，并检查对象存储延迟和 sink 提交时间。"

msgid "Replay memory approaches limit"
msgstr "重放内存接近上限"

msgid "Replay bytes, downstream acknowledgements, checkpoint cadence"
msgstr "重放字节数、下游确认、检查点频率"

msgid ""
"Remove downstream stalls, shorten the durability interval, or raise the "
"limit only with measured memory headroom."
msgstr "消除下游停滞、缩短持久化间隔；只有在测得足够内存余量后，才提高上限。"

msgid "Placement startup times out"
msgstr "放置启动超时"

msgid "Cluster free resources and placement-group bundle"
msgstr "集群空闲资源和 placement-group bundle"

msgid ""
"Reduce requests, add nodes, change placement strategy, or select balanced"
" deployment."
msgstr "减少资源请求、添加节点、更改放置策略，或选择 balanced deployment。"

msgid "Too many tiny output files"
msgstr "微小输出文件过多"

msgid "Checkpoint cadence and rolling thresholds"
msgstr "检查点频率和滚动阈值"

msgid ""
"Increase checkpoint interval/records or file rolling limits while "
"preserving recovery objectives."
msgstr "在满足恢复目标的前提下，提高检查点间隔/记录数或文件滚动限制。"

msgid ""
"Checkpoint cadence is applied per weakly connected physical execution-"
"graph domain, not once per source subtask. All sources in one domain "
"share an epoch; physically disconnected lanes remain independent and can "
"still produce one set of files per lane and interval."
msgstr ""
"检查点节奏按物理执行图的弱连通域应用，而不是按每个源子任务分别应用。同一域中的所有源共享一个 epoch；物理上断开的通道保持独立，仍可按每个通道和间隔生成一组文件。"

msgid "Set operator concurrency"
msgstr "设置算子并发"

msgid ""
"`concurrency` creates physical subtasks for native streaming operators "
"and maps to the relevant Ray Data operation in batch where supported. "
"Choose it from the scarcer of input parallelism, external-service "
"capacity, and cluster resources."
msgstr ""
"`concurrency` 为原生流式算子创建物理子任务，并在批处理中映射到受支持的相应 Ray Data "
"操作。应根据输入并行度、外部服务容量和集群资源中最稀缺的一项来选择其值。"

msgid ""
"Kafka source concurrency above the topic-partition count creates idle "
"subtasks."
msgstr "Kafka 源并发高于 topic 分区数时会产生空闲子任务。"

msgid "Keyed operator concurrency cannot exceed `state.keyed.max-parallelism`."
msgstr "键控算子并发不能超过 `state.keyed.max-parallelism`。"

msgid "Sink concurrency multiplies connections and transaction fan-out."
msgstr "Sink 并发会成倍增加连接数和事务扇出。"

msgid ""
"Increasing concurrency during restore redistributes key groups; it does "
"not change the max-parallelism compatibility value."
msgstr "恢复期间提高并发会重新分配键组，但不会更改 max-parallelism 兼容性值。"

msgid ""
"Keep explicit operator names when comparing plans and metrics across "
"tuning runs. [Autoscaling and live operator rescaling](operator-"
"rescaling.md) explains when a batch concurrency range is dynamic, how to "
"resize a running streaming operator, and why `DataStream.rescale()` does "
"not change parallelism."
msgstr ""
"在不同调优运行之间比较计划和指标时，请保留显式算子名称。[自动伸缩与在线算子扩缩容](operator-"
"rescaling.md)介绍批处理并发范围何时是动态的、如何调整运行中流式算子的并行度，以及 `DataStream.rescale()` "
"为何不会改变并行度。"

msgid "Choose row or batch processing"
msgstr "选择逐行处理或批处理"

msgid ""
"Use `map()` and `flat_map()` for record-oriented logic. Use "
"`map_batches()` when a library benefits from columnar/vectorized input or"
" amortized model calls."
msgstr ""
"面向记录的逻辑请使用 `map()` 和 `flat_map()`。当库能从列式/向量化输入或分摊模型调用成本中受益时，请使用 "
"`map_batches()`。"

msgid ""
"The streaming batch boundary is controlled by an operator's `batch_size` "
"and `batch_timeout`. A large batch improves throughput but increases "
"latency, working memory, checkpoint alignment delay, and replay size. A "
"timeout is required when sparse traffic must not wait indefinitely for a "
"full batch."
msgstr ""
"流式批次边界由算子的 `batch_size` 和 `batch_timeout` "
"控制。大批次可提高吞吐量，但也会增加延迟、工作内存、检查点对齐延迟和重放大小。当稀疏流量不能无限期等待批次填满时，必须设置超时。"

msgid ""
"`pipeline.internal.batch-size`, `pipeline.internal.batch-max-rows`, and "
"`pipeline.internal.batch-max-bytes` control downstream transport micro-"
"batches; they are distinct from a user UDF's batch size. The first "
"reached record, row, byte, or idle-time threshold flushes a target lane. "
"Output row/byte limits and `pipeline.emit-queue.max-batches` are safety "
"bounds, not throughput targets."
msgstr ""
"`pipeline.internal.batch-size`、`pipeline.internal.batch-max-rows` 和 "
"`pipeline.internal.batch-max-bytes` 控制下游传输微批；它们不同于用户 UDF "
"的批大小。记录数、行数、字节数或空闲时间阈值中最先达到的一项会刷新目标通道。输出行/字节限制和 `pipeline.emit-queue.max-"
"batches` 是安全边界，而非吞吐量目标。"

msgid "Operator chaining and columnar passthrough"
msgstr "算子链接与列式直通"

msgid ""
"Operator chaining removes an actor hop only when adjacent operators have "
"a forward edge, matching resource/runtime contracts, no managed state, "
"and no async execution. Disable `pipeline.operator-chaining.enabled` when"
" isolating a hot operator, debugging lifecycle behavior, or assigning "
"different resources."
msgstr ""
"只有当相邻算子具有 forward 边、资源/运行时契约匹配、没有托管状态且没有异步执行时，算子链接才会消除一次 actor "
"跳转。在隔离热点算子、调试生命周期行为或分配不同资源时，请禁用 `pipeline.operator-chaining.enabled`。"

msgid ""
"`pipeline.columnar-passthrough.enabled` is on by default and keeps "
"compatible batches column-oriented across an edge. It removes column-to-"
"row-to-column conversion for batch-heavy UDFs; keyed/custom partitioning "
"still performs row-level slicing. Large duplicated broadcast batches are "
"placed in Ray's Object Store once after `pipeline.transport.object-store-"
"threshold-bytes`."
msgstr ""
"`pipeline.columnar-passthrough.enabled` 默认启用，可让兼容批次跨边保持列式形态。它为批处理密集型 UDF "
"消除列到行再到列的转换；键控/自定义分区仍会执行行级切片。大型重复 broadcast 批次超过 `pipeline.transport"
".object-store-threshold-bytes` 后，只会在 Ray 的 Object Store 中放置一次。"

msgid "Partitioning and skew"
msgstr "分区与倾斜"

msgid ""
"Use `key_by()` only when key affinity or state is required. A hot key "
"remains hot regardless of total parallelism."
msgstr "仅在需要键亲和性或状态时使用 `key_by()`。无论总并行度如何，热点键仍然是热点。"

msgid "Use `round_robin()` for even stateless distribution."
msgstr "使用 `round_robin()` 均匀分配无状态工作。"

msgid ""
"Use `rescale()` to limit edge fan-out when upstream/downstream "
"concurrency ratios align."
msgstr "当上游/下游并发比例合适时，使用 `rescale()` 限制边扇出。"

msgid ""
"Use `broadcast()` only for small streams; its network and processing cost"
" multiplies by downstream concurrency."
msgstr "仅对小型流使用 `broadcast()`；其网络和处理成本会随下游并发成倍增加。"

msgid ""
"`adaptive_shuffle()` reacts to downstream write timeouts. It cannot "
"repair a logically hot key whose state must stay on one subtask."
msgstr "`adaptive_shuffle()` 会响应下游写入超时，但无法修复状态必须保留在单个子任务上的逻辑热点键。"

msgid ""
"For batch execution, use `stream.data.repartition`, sorting, or the "
"matching Ray Data operation; Klein streaming partitioners do not tune Ray"
" Data partitions."
msgstr ""
"对于批执行，请使用 `stream.data.repartition`、排序或相应的 Ray Data 操作；Klein 流式分区器不会调优 "
"Ray Data 分区。"

msgid "State backend and checkpoints"
msgstr "状态后端与检查点"

msgid ""
"Memory state has low overhead for moderate state. RocksDB moves mutation-"
"heavy state to node-local storage and is usually preferable when state no"
" longer fits comfortably in worker memory. Put its local directory on "
"fast disposable SSD."
msgstr ""
"对于中等大小的状态，内存状态开销较低。RocksDB 将变更密集型状态移至节点本地存储；当状态已无法轻松容纳于 worker "
"内存时，通常更适合使用 RocksDB。请将其本地目录放在快速、可丢弃的 SSD 上。"

msgid ""
"The Object Store snapshot cache avoids repeatedly moving large immutable "
"snapshots through coordinator memory. Lowering its minimum size caches "
"more objects but increases Object Store metadata and capacity pressure."
msgstr ""
"Object Store 快照缓存可避免大型不可变快照反复经过协调器内存。降低其最小大小会缓存更多对象，但会增加 Object Store "
"元数据和容量压力。"

msgid "Checkpoint cadence is a recovery-time objective:"
msgstr "检查点频率是一项恢复时间目标："

msgid ""
"shorter intervals reduce the replay window and time since the last "
"durable state, but add barrier, snapshot, storage, and sink-commit "
"overhead;"
msgstr "更短的间隔可缩小重放窗口和距上次持久状态的时间，但会增加屏障、快照、存储和 sink 提交开销；"

msgid ""
"longer intervals improve steady-state throughput but increase recovery "
"work and pending external transactions."
msgstr "更长的间隔可提高稳态吞吐量，但会增加恢复工作和待处理外部事务。"

msgid ""
"Record and duration triggers race; whichever fires first resets both. Do "
"not disable both unless the job intentionally accepts no periodic "
"recovery point or checkpoint-driven sink publication."
msgstr "记录数触发器和持续时间触发器会竞速；任一先触发都会重置两者。除非作业有意不接受周期性恢复点或检查点驱动的 sink 发布，否则不要同时禁用两者。"

msgid "Replay and backpressure bounds"
msgstr "重放与背压边界"

msgid ""
"The replay buffer keeps output until downstream progress confirms it is "
"safe to drop. `pipeline.replay-buffer.max-bytes` is a hard guard: "
"exceeding it fails the task into normal recovery before process OOM. "
"Raising it should be the last step after fixing stalled acknowledgements "
"and verifying node memory."
msgstr ""
"重放缓冲区会保留输出，直到下游进度确认可以安全丢弃。`pipeline.replay-buffer.max-bytes` "
"是硬性保护：超过该值会在进程 OOM 前使任务失败并进入正常恢复。只有修复停滞的确认并验证节点内存后，才应最后考虑提高该值。"

msgid ""
"`pipeline.input-buffer.size` and `pipeline.input-buffer.max-bytes` bound "
"logical rows and estimated payload bytes. One oversized columnar block is"
" admitted only into an otherwise empty inbox. The same dual bound applies"
" to output buffering, so wide records cannot bypass a row-only limit."
msgstr ""
"`pipeline.input-buffer.size` 和 `pipeline.input-buffer.max-bytes` "
"限制逻辑行数和估算的载荷字节数。一个超大列式块只能进入原本为空的 inbox。同样的双重边界也适用于输出缓冲，因此宽记录无法绕过仅基于行数的限制。"

msgid ""
"After every change, compare throughput, tail latency, checkpoint "
"duration, failure recovery time, and peak memory. Keep the change only "
"when the full job, not one isolated operator, improves."
msgstr "每次变更后，都要比较吞吐量、尾延迟、检查点持续时间、故障恢复时间和内存峰值。只有整个作业而非单个孤立算子得到改善时，才保留该变更。"
